title: Musashi Miyamot Trilogy EngSubs
description:
This is the Musashi Miyamoto trilogy made by Hiroshi Inagaki in 1954-56.  

Starring the inimitable Toshiro Mifune as the legendary samurai, it is also 

widely known as the Samurai trilogy. This particular set has been put together 

from diverse sources. Sound has been synchronised. English subtitles 

synchronised and embedded. To the best of my knowledge it is a unique set. 

Enjoy watching and please seed generously and long.
